summary: An ordinance refunding to G. Kinnear Co. the sum of $30.00 out of the Elliott Avenue Condemnation Fund, Ordinance No. 12818, which amount represents an excess in said fund occasioned by surrender of transcript of judgment in Cause No. 867, by said G. Kinnear Co. (in error) off-setting the condemnation assessment against lot 13, block 151, Seattle Tide Lands; which said assessment was afterwards paid by the rightful owners (Richmond-Burnett Co.) on January 30, 1909, as evidenced by Treasurer's receipt No. T. 4471.
